be.ac.ulb.infof307.g10.models.database

Class Database

  • java.lang.Object
    • be.ac.ulb.infof307.g10.models.database.Database

  • public final class Database
extends Object
    Object to manage AbstractObject persistence. This database is working only with AbstractObjects because save method needs an auto generated id. General way to access this class is using a DAO. For more information about internal behavior, please see official JPA documentation.
